import React from 'react'
import EachDeal from '../Components/EachDeals'
function EditIngPage() {
  return (
    <>
      <EachDeal/>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/deal/:dealId" element={<EachDeal />} />
        <Route path="/package/:packageId" element={<Eacj />} />
      </Routes>
    </>
  )
}

export default EditIngPage
